 " into a sequence of Hadamard and phase gates ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["Z", "k"], "\[DotEqual]", 
    RowBox[{"(", GridBox[{
       {"1", "0"},
       {"0", 
